data.description: Charming house with loads of potential either for 1st time homebuyers or investors.  Original hardwood floors!  Extra deep lot with alley access in the back, so there is potential for additional units, a detached garage, or some other expansion.  Concrete RV pad with hook-ups .  Detached storage shed which is large enough to be a work shop.
